These are the shortcuts Bernie thinks are kinda cool

ALT + SHIFT + F : Autoformat
CTRL + SHIFT + P : Opens Pallete
CTRL + SHIFT + O : Organize Imports 
CTRL + SHIFT + \ : Jumps to Paired Bracket
ALT + Z : Word Wrap Toggle
CTRL + SPACE : Suggestion
CTRL + . : Iterate through errors
F2 : Full page refractor


Right Click commands or subsystems and select "create new class/command" to do just that
Right click on an import error, select "Source Action" then "organize imports"
